              urlEndpoint: {
                url: "/watch"
              }
            },
            playerResponse: {
              playabilityStatus: {
                status: 'OK'
              }
            },
            response: {
              contents: {
                twoColumnWatchNextResults: {
                  results: {
                    results: {
                      contents: [{
                        videoPrimaryInfoRenderer: {},
                        videoSecondaryInfoRenderer: {}
                      }]
                    }
                  },
                  secondaryResults: {
                    secondaryResults: {}
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        };

        window.ytcfg.set('FILLER_DATA', fillerData);
      };

        window.getPageData = function() {
          if (window.ytcsi) {window.ytcsi.tick("pr", null, '');}
          var endpoint = null;
            endpoint = {"commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/watch?v=br36gZeC49M","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_WATCH","rootVe":3832}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"/watch?v=br36gZeC49M"}};
          var data = {
              page: "watch",
              player: ytplayer.config,
              playerResponse: window.ytInitialPlayerResponse,
                url: "\/watch?v=br36gZeC49M",
              response: window.ytInitialData,
              endpoint: endpoint
          };
          return {
            data: data,
            endpoint: endpoint
          };
        };

        if (window.loadDataHook) {
          var pageData = window.getPageData();
          window.loadDataHook(pageData.endpoint, pageData.data);
          window.loadDataHook = null;
        }
        setFiller();

    })();


  </script>
